Read in data

SAPE (Controls vs 4hr)

According to the (benchling)[https://freenome.benchling.com/freenome/f/lib_rLUfj3iF-06-guardbanding-for-automation/etr_sY3wzurA-bwtm-beta-lot-sa-pe-room-temperature-stability-0-4-hour/edit], the plate 2 or P2 in the file_name the SAPE is prepared 4 hours earlier.

We only need to focus on the top 7 proteins of interest.

How many outliers AFTER bead failure?

Can we find out how many times the following occurred?

  1. Bead count failed AND after removing that well, there was still an outlier?
  2. How many times there were bead failures in the same batch and same standard?
